## Upgrade Flow (Manual Until ~10 Paying Users)

1. User clicks "Upgrade to Pro" → lands on PayPal subscription page
2. User subscribes → PayPal emails you confirmation
3. You run in Supabase SQL Editor:
```sql
UPDATE profiles SET plan = 'pro' WHERE email = 'their@email.com';
```
4. User now has unlimited proposals — `FREE_LIMIT` check passes because `plan = 'pro'`

---

## Learning Loop — How to Trigger

1. Generate 3+ proposals
2. Click outcome button on each (Hired / No Response / Rejected)
3. Send POST to `/api/learn` — use browser console:
```javascript
fetch('/api/learn', { method: 'POST' }).then(r => r.json()).then(console.log)
```
4. Check `forge_rules` table in Supabase — should see a new row with `source = 'learned'`
5. Next proposal generated will automatically use the new rule in its system prompt

